data.name: AWS Kinesis
data.description: Amazon Kinesis is an Amazon Web Service for easy and scalable collection, processing, and analysis of video and data streams in real-time. It can also be used for batch processing. It is can be used for data ingestion for machine learning, analytics, and other applications.

data.name: AWS IoT Core
data.description: AWS IoT provides the cloud services that connect your IoT devices to other devices and AWS cloud services. AWS IoT provides device software that can help you integrate your IoT devices into AWS IoT-based solutions. If your devices can connect to AWS IoT, AWS IoT can connect them to the cloud services that AWS provides.
